            <title>[LU-3637] build Lustre with Intel OFED for Xeon Phi</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3637</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The compilation of Lustre with Intel OFED for Xeon Phi failed because of missing include of pci-dma.h header file. In Linux kernel includes this file included automatically from pci.h but in Intel Xeon Phi headers it&apos;s not true.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
